title: Crock pot Chicken and Vegetables
directions: Wash and place green beans on one side of the Crockpot. Place cut potatoes on the other side and the chicken in the center. Mix together the Dry Mixes and Sprinkle evenly over the chicken. Place the 1/2 of butter on top. Slowly pour water on vegetables (not chicken). Cook on low heat for 6-8 hours until chicken is done and tender
ingredients: 5 medium red potatoes (cut up in chunks)
